# cte-inline-filter-scan

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `cte_inlining_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (cte ?name ?def (filter ?pred (scan ?name)))
rhs: (filter ?pred ?def)
